[1] Cholera - China
Date: Tue, 13 Sep 2005
From: ProMED-mail <promed@promedmail.org>
Source: People's Daily Online [edited]
<http://english1.people.com.cn/200509/13/eng20050913_208313.html>

China's Ministry of Health issued on Mon, 12 Sep 2005, a report on
nationwide epidemic situation in Aug 2005. Statistics of the ministry
showed more cases of cholera occurred in the month compared with the
same period of 2005. The number of cholera cases was 116, much
higher than the same period of 2004. [The higher numbers were mainly
the result of] several big epidemic outbreaks due to dinner parties
in rural areas.
--
ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>
